  ‚úÖ Stock up + commodity up = Fundamental strength (HIGH confidence)
  ‚ö†Ô∏è Stock down + commodity up = Profit-taking or technical (BUY opportunity?)
  ‚ö†Ô∏è Stock up + commodity down = Speculation or divergence (CAUTION)
