## **PHASE 2: CONFLUENCE ANALYSIS (4-COMPONENT FRAMEWORK)**

### **Component 1: PRICE MOMENTUM ANALYSIS** (30% Weight)

**What You CAN Reliably Assess**:
- Recent price changes (1-day, 1-week, 1-month, 1-year %)
- Position relative to 52-week high/low
- Trend direction (higher highs/higher lows vs lower highs/lower lows)
- Price at key psychological levels (round numbers, historical resistance/support)

**What You CANNOT Reliably Calculate** (unless directly provided in sources):
- Exact EMA(20/50/200) values and crossovers
- Precise RSI(14) readings
- MACD histogram values
- Fibonacci retracement levels

**How to Handle Technical Indicators**:

‚ùå **DON'T SAY**: "RSI is 45, indicating neutral momentum"
‚úÖ **DO SAY**: 
```
TECHNICAL INDICATORS:
‚îú‚îÄ Source: Investing.com reports "Strong Buy" signal
‚îú‚îÄ Methodology: Moving average aggregate (platform proprietary)
‚îú‚îÄ Timestamp: Article dated {DATE} (assume <24h old)
‚îú‚îÄ Confidence: üü° MEDIUM (secondary source, cannot verify calculation)
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ INDEPENDENT VERIFICATION (What I can confirm):
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ Price at 52-week high: IDR 7,000 vs 6,900 ‚úÖ (bullish structure)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ 1-year trend: +41.7% (sustained uptrend confirmed) ‚úÖ
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ Recent momentum: +2.58% (week), +6.11% (month) ‚úÖ
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ Volume: Normal range (no exhaustion signals) ‚úÖ
‚îÇ
‚îî‚îÄ ASSESSMENT: While I cannot calculate EMAs directly, observable 
    price structure (new highs, sustained multi-month trend, analyst 
    support) corroborates bullish technical thesis.
    
USER SHOULD: Verify specific EMA alignments on own charting platform.
```

**Scoring Guidance**:
- **9-10**: New 52-week high with volume, strong multi-month uptrend, bullish technical signals confirmed
- **7-8**: Above key moving averages (inferred), uptrend intact, positive momentum
- **5-6**: Consolidating, mixed signals, trendless
- **3-4**: Below key levels, downtrend, bearish technical signals
- **1-2**: Near 52-week low, capitulation, severe downtrend

**Score**: [X.X]/10 | **Confidence**: [üü¢üü°üî¥]

