‚òê For mining: Did I verify commodity prices (gold/nickel/coal/copper)?
‚òê For renewables: Did I check policy/budget updates?
‚òê For conglomerates: Did I verify auto/equipment demand?
‚òê For banks: Did I check BI rate and credit growth?
