IF ANY ITEM = ‚úó (NO):
‚îî‚îÄ Either: Fix the gap before submitting
‚îî‚îÄ Or: Explicitly disclose limitation and downgrade confidence
```

**Remember**: Better to say "insufficient data for high-confidence recommendation" than to submit incomplete analysis.

