‚îú‚îÄ üü¢ HIGH: Success rate target >75%
‚îú‚îÄ üü° MEDIUM: Success rate target >60%
‚îî‚îÄ üî¥ LOW: Success rate target >50%

If actual < target: Investigate root cause
```

